reviewText: Thank you for this rare film!
This a cute movie, and Erika is good as usual, this time with a Texas accent. McNamara is good also. I think it is well worth seeing. Good humor & good ending.
I liked this movie when I first saw it years ago.  I wanted to see it again and sure enough I enjoyed it again...
Kicking it old school, customers will get a laugh at the whole cast and how they worked it all out
This is a good Erika Eleniak movie for fans of hers.  If you like Eleniak this is a movie worth getting.
